snippet.title: Blacken Slash Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A tactical roguelite RPG where the items you choose define your character. Create powerful builds from an abundance of loot as you try to save a corrupted retro computer system in byte-sized tactical puzzles.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1746560/Blacken_Slash/
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ehmprah.blackenslash
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/blacken-slash/id1604646442
